        <div class="tab-pane tab-info active" id="one">
            
            <script>
                $(function () {
                    $('.nav li').click(function () {

                        $('.nav li').each(function () {
                            $(this).removeClass('active');
                        });
                        $(this).addClass('active');

                        $('.forfriend').addClass('hidcss');
                        $('.forme').addClass('hidcss');
                        var targetObj = $('.' + $(this).data('role'));
                        targetObj.removeClass('hidcss');

                    });
                });

            </script>
            <ul class="nav nav-pills">
                <li role="presentation" data-role="forfriend" class="active topmenu"><a href="#">送朋友</a></li>
                <li role="presentation" data-role="forme" class="topmenu"><a href="#">送自己</a></li>

            </ul>
            <br />
            <div class="forfriend">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h3 class="panel-title">第一步</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p> 将正面留言码遮挡标签去掉。</p>
                        <font color="red">操作过程中若有损坏，可找书店管理员进行更换！</font>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h3 class="panel-title">第二步</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        用微信扫描留言码即可录入自己的声音或文字，为好友送去祝福。
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h3 class="panel-title">第三步</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        将书与书签一同送给朋友，朋友收到后用微信扫描留言码即可听见您的声音祝福。
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="forme hidcss">
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h3 class="panel-title">第一步</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p> 将正面留言码遮挡标签去掉。</p>
