                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h3 class="panel-title">第二步</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        用微信扫描留言码即可录入声音或文字，记录自己此时此刻的心情。
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel panel-default">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h3 class="panel-title">第三步</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        将书与书签一起珍藏。（将声音与文字也一起珍藏）
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>
</div>
<div class="btnpanel">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-info ect-colorf button_only" onclick="btn_ok()">点击试用</button>

</div>